WEBVTT

00:00:00.931 --> 00:00:03.517
I was around 10 when one day,

00:00:03.541 --> 00:00:06.284
I discovered a box
of my father's old things.

00:00:06.985 --> 00:00:09.815
In it, under a bunch
of his college textbooks,

00:00:09.839 --> 00:00:14.311
was a pair of black corduroy
bell-bottom pants.

00:00:15.292 --> 00:00:17.155
These pants were awful --

00:00:17.179 --> 00:00:19.176
musty and moth-eaten.

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:21.256
And of course, I fell in love with them.

00:00:21.770 --> 00:00:23.395
I'd never seen anything like them.

00:00:24.154 --> 00:00:25.623
Until that day,

00:00:25.647 --> 00:00:30.137
all I'd ever known and worn
was my school uniform,